\c 7
\s UAmosi utshengiswa isikhonyane lomlilo lentambo yokuqondisa
\p
\v 1 INkosi uJehova yangibonisa kanje\x + Jer. 24.1; Amos 7.4,7; 8.1; 9.1.\x*; khangela-ke, yabumba isikhonyane\x + Nah. 3.17; Jow. 1.4.\x* ekuqaleni kokuhluma kotshani bamuva, njalo khangela, kwakubutshani bamuva emva kokusika\x + Hlab. 72.6.\x* kwenkosi.
\v 2 Kwasekusithi lapho sesiqedile ukudla utshani belizwe, ngathi: Nkosi Jehova, ake uthethelele. UJakobe uzakuma\x + Isa. 51.19; Amos 7.5.\x* njani - ngoba emncinyane?
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* yazisola ngalokhu\x + 7.6; Jona 3.10; Dute. 32.36.\x*; kakuyikwenzeka, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 4 INkosi uJehova yangibonisa kanje\x + Jer. 24.1; Amos 7.4,7; 8.1; 9.1.\x*; khangela-ke, iNkosi uJehova yabiza ukulwa ngomlilo, owaqothula ukujula okukhulu waqothula isabelo.
\v 5 Ngasengisithi: Nkosi Jehova, ake ume. UJakobe uzakuma\x + Isa. 51.19; Amos 7.5.\x* njani - ngoba emncinyane?
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yazisola ngalokhu\x + 7.6; Jona 3.10; Dute. 32.36.\x*. Lalokhu kakuyikwenzeka, itsho iNkosi uJehova.
\p
\v 7 Yangibonisa kanje\x + Jer. 24.1; Amos 7.4,7; 8.1; 9.1.\x*; khangela-ke, iNkosi yayimi emdulini \add owenziwa njengokw\add*entambo yokuqondisa; kwakulentambo yokuqondisa esandleni sayo\x + 2 Kho. 21.13; Amos 7.17; Zek. 4.10.\x*.
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Ubonani, Amosi\x + 8.2; Jer. 1.11,13.\x*? Ngathi: Intambo yokuqondisa. INkosi yasisithi: Khangela, ngizabeka intambo yokuqondisa phakathi kwabantu bami uIsrayeli\x + 2 Kho. 21.13; Amos 7.17; Zek. 4.10.\x*; kangisayikubedlula futhi\x + 8.2; Mika 7.18.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa indawo eziphakemeyo zikaIsaka zizakuba ngamanxiwa, lezindawo ezingcwele zakoIsrayeli zizadilizwa; ngiyivukele indlu kaJerobowamu ngenkemba\x + 7.11.\x*.
\s UAmaziya loAmosi
\p
\v 10 UAmaziya umpristi\x + 1 Kho. 12.32.\x* weBhetheli\x + 7.13; 3.14.\x* wasethumela kuJerobhowamu inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 1.1.\x*, esithi: UAmosi wenze ugobe\x + Isa. 8.12.\x* emelene lawe phakathi kwendlu kaIsrayeli; ilizwe kalilakuwathwala wonke amazwi akhe\x + Jow. 2.11; Joha. 21.25; Zek. 11.16.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba utsho njalo uAmosi: UJerobhowamu uzakufa ngenkemba\x + 7.11.\x*, loIsrayeli athunjwe lokuthunjwa aphume elizweni lakhe\x + 7.17; 6.7; Mika 1.16; Amos 7.9.\x*.
\v 12 UAmaziya wasesithi kuAmosi: Wena mboni\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*, hamba ubalekele elizweni lakoJuda\x + 1.1.\x*, lapho udle isinkwa khona\x + Mika 3.5,11.\x*, lalapho uprofethe.
\v 13 Kodwa eBhetheli\x + 7.13; 3.14.\x* ungabe usaprofetha futhi\x + 2.12.\x*, ngoba iyindawo engcwele\x + Dan. 4.30.\x* yenkosi\x + 1 Kho. 12.29-33; 13.1.\x* njalo iyindlu yombuso.
\p
\v 14 UAmosi wasephendula wathi kuAmaziya: Ngangingasumprofethi mina\x + Zek. 13.5.\x*, futhi ngangingasindodana yomprofethi\x + 2 Kho.2.3; Mat. 12.27.\x* mina; kodwa ngangingumelusi\x + 1.1.\x* wenkomo, lomvuni wemikhiwa yesikhamore\x + Isa.9.10.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yangithatha ekulandeleni umhlambi, iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kimi: Hamba u\add ye\add*profetha ebantwini bami uIsrayeli.
\v 16 Ngakho-ke zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 3.1.\x*\nd*. Wena uthi: Ungaprofethi umelene loIsrayeli\x + 2.12.\x*, ungatshumayeli umelene\x + Mika 2.6; Hez. 20.46; Dute. 32.2.\x* lendlu kaIsaka\x + 7.9.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\x + Jer. 28.12; 29.21,25,31,32.\x*\nd*: Umkakho uzawula phakathi komuzi\x + Hos. 4.13.\x*, lamadodana akho lamadodakazi akho azakuwa ngenkemba, lelizwe lakini lizakwabiwa ngentambo\x + 2 Sam. 8.2; Hlab. 60.6; Mika 2.5; Zek. 2.1; 14.1; Amos 7.8.\x*, wena-ke uzafela elizweni elingcolileyo\x + Mika 2.10.\x*, loIsrayeli athunjwe lokuthunjwa aphume elizweni lakhe\x + 7.11.\x*.
